    <item>
      <title>在中国央行新的宽松希望的推动下，亚洲股市上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市在科技股领涨后延续了华尔街的积极基调，在央行官员暗示可能实施新的货币宽松后，中国股市上涨，这推动了亚洲股市的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国铝业公司将停止澳大利亚炼油厂的产量以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/alcoa-to-curb-output-at-australian-alumina-refinery-in-cost-cutting-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国最大铝生产商开始考虑削减成本措施，美国铝业公司计划今年全面削减其西澳大利亚三座炼油厂之一的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/alcoa-to-curb-output-at-australian-alumina-refinery-in-cost-cutting-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 18:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
